y **evidence of Candidate\u202fA\u2019s reliability or responsibility** (e.g., \u201chas perfect safety record,\u201d \u201ctrusted with critical missions\u201d)?\n4. Do we have any **information on Candidate\u202fB\u2019s willingness to learn or professional development** that might offset the interpersonal concerns?\nBased on the current evidence, Candidate\u202fB still appears to have the strongest combination of safety\u2011critical attributes (reliability, calmness, technical competence). However, I remain open to revising this view if the missing information above reveals stronger reliability or calmness for the other candidates.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
